{"tid":456083,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PVP遊戲根本係講天份","createTime":"2017-11-02T16:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T03:50:02.000Z","uid":19657,"like":73,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"d5635a7b13df5c72f09380cdb935c41d2f48a012","tid":456083,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:03:11.000Z","msg":"唔存在玩得耐就叻啲呢種講法<br />\n你只係係你嘅能力內有進步<br />\n但之後再爬極都會有一個上限<br />\n<br />\n你以為你勁，其實只係殺咗啲天份比你低嘅人<br />\n你以為你廢，其實只係天份高嘅人比你更掌握大局<br />\n<br />\n反應力、警覺性、心理質素，全部係無得量化嘅嘢<br />\n再多嘅時間你都唔可以同班打比賽嘅人持平<br />\n因為人地天份就係高，無點解"},{"pid":"70a14a57f7a6758f2c244dc6caf9c57982f0b1f1","tid":456083,"uid":11254,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:05:38.000Z","msg":"你咁講全部運動比賽都係架喇<br />\n你有得練到美斯咁勁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"014d23446d0355eefe75d867be7da3d2072c7a95","tid":456083,"uid":19657,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:10:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咁講全部運動比賽都係架喇<br />\n你有得練到美斯咁勁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我最後打漏咗段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以pvp唔係遊戲，係現實<br />\n玩輸咗唔好唔開心，應該反而怪隻game<br />\n點解將你分配畀啲天份高你咁多嘅人"},{"pid":"8696343dcada8251a6358578d9e8d7750f2cf0d6","tid":456083,"uid":693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:12:28.000Z","msg":"睇下咩PVP GAME啦"},{"pid":"9b75c8d62e651f93721fc16faa008194be3ef6b9","tid":456083,"uid":39889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:13:30.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n所以有d game就算幾hit,幾多人玩<br />\n玩兩玩發覺唔岩自己都冇再玩<br />\n淨係玩d自己算比較叻既game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548cfcf4a9905a4d4e10466d60545776d9d3f3cc","tid":456083,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:16:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下咩PVP GAME啦</blockquote><br />\nmoba，fps都一定係架啦<br />\n<b